CountryCode.org is your complete guide to make a call from anywhere in the world, to anywhere in the world. This page details Philippines phone code.

The Philippines country code 63 will allow you to call Philippines from another country. Philippines telephone code 63 is dialed after the IDD. Philippines international dialing 63 is followed by an area code.

The Philippines area code table below shows the various city codes for Philippines. Philippines country codes are followed by these area codes. With the complete Philippines dialing code, you can make your international call.
